{"tid":2180952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大律師公會去信法援署署長 冀重視大律師與被告建立的互信關係","createTime":"2020-08-30T08:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T10:15:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4950c10a9e99c0be78f42e4f62fc857ebb8b4c19","tid":2180952,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/EGFY5RMT4JEKTJQOM6QHJNRZVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FEGFY5RMT4JEKTJQOM6QHJNRZVE%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=064995eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FEGFY5RMT4JEKTJQOM6QHJNRZVE%2F&h=d3f4c115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/EGFY5RMT4JEKTJQOM6QHJNRZVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年反修例運動至今，多達662人被控暴動罪。香港大律師公會透露，收到3宗會員投訴，全部均被法援署以經驗不足、或處理區域法院案件不足夠等為理由，拒絕有關律師繼續代表暴動罪案件的被告。公會指本月初已去信法援署署長，盼署方可重視大律師與被告之間已建立的互信關係。<br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會法律援助改革委員會主席譚俊傑透露，公會收到3宗會員投訴，相關大律師一直跟進被告的案件，但法援署以律師經驗不足，或處理區域法院案件不足夠等為理由，拒絕有關律師繼續代表暴動罪案件的被告，「律師一直跟緊單案件，但法援署以佢哋經驗不足、或區域法院做嘅案件唔夠，甚至有啲冇畀原因，拒絕委派佢哋代表被告，要求委派其他大律師或律師畀被告人。」<br />\n<br />\n有代表暴動案被告的大律師稱以病人看醫生作比喻，「你睇開一個醫生，佢一直都醫緊你，就嚟做手術，但突然間話要轉醫生」，直言法援署未有考慮被告人的想法，「法援署點解要做到咁絕，令到當事人冇咗依靠、信心，法援到底係幫人，定幫你想幫嘅人呢？」"},{"pid":"0af5ac791a9b1852ac0a6be39ea1ab0c327acd73","tid":2180952,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c7a9d4cd4a8c90860187f95b659811f202fde9","tid":2180952,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"招喚會員「恆屍」"},{"pid":"0f1a3938acb16d6278650336965101119f040ca5","tid":2180952,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af5ac791a9b1852ac0a6be39ea1ab0c327acd73","tid":2180952,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431497965fa513e888d965bd98d0895def58ab0e","tid":2180952,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea0f0d4c08b6ada2ab7d5a40b77df0586fa32a5","tid":2180952,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c3e62d7ffdc617d4dfbc10eb17535c0c666969","tid":2180952,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e6b4acc97cb659c6cfef2fbcfeb0fc7a23df51","tid":2180952,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"omdb"},{"pid":"2cc9926945908fff3aed9e1f566d3e28d418ba85","tid":2180952,"uid":323319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f746864dc90a96b6c4ed77f18eb61fa03a3d31c7","tid":2180952,"uid":29